subject: Football
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: G. J. Kinne passed for 346 yards and 3 touchdowns for Tulsa (10-3) in a 62-35 victory over No. 24 Hawaii (10-4) at the Hawaii Bowl in Honolulu.
